00:08:11.966 --> 00:08:13.166
The Zichen Hall exploded.

00:08:13.646 --> 00:08:15.206
His Majesty and Xiao Yicheng

00:08:15.206 --> 00:08:16.446
were blown to pieces.

00:08:16.446 --> 00:08:18.966
Impossible! I don't believe it.

00:08:19.366 --> 00:08:22.006
His Majesty knew Xiao Yicheng
would refine him into elixirs,

00:08:22.206 --> 00:08:24.886
