00:08:41.646 --> 00:08:43.206
he gave you an edict of succession.

00:08:44.166 --> 00:08:46.086
After he and Xiao Yicheng die,

00:08:46.086 --> 00:08:47.606
with the edict of succession,

00:08:47.606 --> 00:08:49.286
